title: We Recap Our Weekend + We Debate Whether Or Not Gift Giving Is Selfish
description:
Is gift giving selfish? One rapper explained why he thinks it is. So today, we're going to share our thoughts on his comments.
But first, this weekend was major for us! From our Back To School event to our Bert's Big Adventure summer reunion, we had a blast!
